| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1718 — Recovery Inhibition (bert)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6fee4fe8-a9e1-51c8-8eb0-b62bdbc4e951"
